videos.description: 1H (5:10) ND Demetrius Jackson Steal.
videos.headline: Demetrius Jackson capitalizes on a lazy Duke inbound; Jackson fouled going up by Brandon Ingram and would make both foul shots.

videos.description: Off a Notre Dame turnover, Duke goes end-to-end in a flash, finishing with Grayson Allen throwing down the huge one-handed slam.
videos.headline: No dribbles needed for Allen's monster jam

videos.description: Duke's Brandon Ingram cuts down the lane and puts up a layup that Notre Dame's Zach Auguste sends into the stratosphere with a vicious block.
videos.headline: Auguste with one of the most vicious blocks of the season
